# 📷 CameraX Custom Camera App (Kotlin)

This Android app demonstrates a **custom camera screen** built with **CameraX** and **Kotlin**, supporting:

- Fullscreen camera preview
- Manual photo capture (shutter button)
- Zoom slider (1x to 5x)
- Manual focus slider (fallback to auto-focus)
- Tap-to-focus functionality
- 3x3 rule-of-thirds grid overlay (drawn programmatically)
- Supports Android 10 to 16 (API 29 to 35)

---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Fullscreen live camera preview
✅ Photo capture and local image saving
✅ Zoom slider (up to 5x)
✅ Focus slider (simulated with tap-to-focus metering)
✅ Tap-to-focus gesture
✅ Grid overlay using custom `View`
✅ Runtime permissions handling
✅ Compatible with Android 10 (Q) to 15/16

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- Kotlin
- Android CameraX
- Jetpack Lifecycle
- AndroidX View and Preview APIs

